name: freemindviewer2
description: - Usage   - call index.html   - with get-parameters     - path (path to folder containing the mindmap-file)     - map (name of the file including extension ".mm")     - list (boolean to show data as list or as mindmap)   - example     - ..../index.html?path=/mm&map=README.mm&list=false     - shows map "README" in mm folder as mindmap
author: Dennis Hawran
